name: Hallow Meemmo
description:
It's Halloween and Mimmo loves it because he can make jokes with his name. He's got a pumpkin helmet and a brave soul. 

He usually hangs out in a cafè named "Ciao Belli", because of its Italian roots.

In there, they were all saying "have you heard of the hidden broken Gameboy?" 

Everyone inside the cafè was talking about it, so he got curious and started investigating himself...
